WEBVTT

00:11.270 --> 00:12.320
You still dare?

00:11.550 --> 00:13.880
[1997]

00:13.020 --> 00:14.750
That's for bullying my sister!

00:15.820 --> 00:16.830
It's fine now.

00:17.830 --> 00:18.920
How did you cut your leg?

00:18.920 --> 00:20.280
Stop! What's going on?

00:20.280 --> 00:21.320
Stop fighting!

00:21.320 --> 00:22.320
What's wrong with you?

00:22.320 --> 00:23.050
Are you okay?

00:23.120 --> 00:24.520
Which class are you from?

00:24.800 --> 00:25.920
At your age, and you're

00:25.920 --> 00:27.320
already picking fights?

00:27.830 --> 00:28.870
Call your class teacher here.

00:28.870 --> 00:30.730
He was fighting,
and you just stood there watching?

00:30.730 --> 00:32.159
Call your class teacher here immediately!

00:32.159 --> 00:33.760
Don't you know how to reason?

00:34.560 --> 00:35.640
Can fighting solve the problem?

00:35.640 --> 00:36.070
Dad.

00:36.070 --> 00:37.150
Dad. Dad.

00:37.150 --> 00:38.520
Dad, don't hit them.

00:38.520 --> 00:39.710
Don't hit my brothers anymore.

00:39.710 --> 00:40.640
Stand properly.

00:41.070 --> 00:42.470
I haven't even scolded you yet.

00:42.470 --> 00:44.200
Uncle, stop hitting.

00:44.320 --> 00:45.430
They were not wrong.

00:45.430 --> 00:46.670
That guy's made a habit

00:46.670 --> 00:47.920
of bullying Zhou Jin.

00:48.070 --> 00:49.880
We've put up with him for a long time.

00:49.880 --> 00:51.710
Yes, we've put up
with him for a long time.

00:51.710 --> 00:53.040
Don't hit them anymore.

00:53.200 --> 00:54.200
Cut the crap.

00:54.200 --> 00:55.200
Hurry up and go home.

00:55.200 --> 00:57.000
Yan Bin, Zhan Wei,

00:57.110 --> 00:58.110
stop talking.

00:58.600 --> 00:59.660
Hurry up and leave.

01:05.510 --> 01:07.000
You've got some nerve.

01:08.590 --> 01:10.250
Stirring up trouble nonstop.

01:10.920 --> 01:12.840
You're almost a celebrity in school.

01:12.840 --> 01:13.870
Dad.

01:14.000 --> 01:16.280
Dad, don't hit my brothers anymore.

01:16.280 --> 01:18.560
Don't hit them anymore.

01:18.710 --> 01:20.590
Stop hitting.

01:21.400 --> 01:22.680
Okay.

01:23.780 --> 01:25.430
And you, little troublemaker.

01:25.430 --> 01:26.840
Grow up already.

01:26.870 --> 01:29.270
Stop making your brothers worry about you.

01:29.810 --> 01:30.740
Stand properly.

02:55.020 --> 03:00.660
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

03:00.930 --> 03:03.380
[Episode 18]

03:11.360 --> 03:11.870
Okay.

03:12.150 --> 03:13.150
Just bury it here.

03:32.280 --> 03:33.470
I got your message.

03:36.200 --> 03:37.860
How many do you want this time?

03:39.470 --> 03:40.600
Such a large amount?

03:41.840 --> 03:42.900
When do you need it?

03:44.870 --> 03:46.630
No, it's too risky right now.

03:47.350 --> 03:49.320
Don't worry. Let me think of a way.

03:49.870 --> 03:50.590
Anyway, the method we used last time

03:50.590 --> 03:51.560
is definitely

03:51.560 --> 03:52.590
not going to work.

04:09.590 --> 04:10.190
Chief Tan.

04:10.270 --> 04:10.940
Satellite phone.

04:10.940 --> 04:11.800
Put it through.

04:17.720 --> 04:18.750
Are you nearby?

04:22.750 --> 04:23.160
Yes.

04:23.160 --> 04:24.420
When do you plan to act?

04:24.480 --> 04:25.740
As soon as we're ready,

04:25.750 --> 04:26.430
we'll act immediately.

04:26.430 --> 04:26.800
No.

04:27.600 --> 04:28.370
Don't act yet.

04:28.370 --> 04:29.750
Old Scorpion isn't here.

04:29.750 --> 04:30.610
Where did he go?

04:31.000 --> 04:31.680
I don't know, either.

04:31.680 --> 04:33.140
I just found out he's gone.

04:33.280 --> 04:34.140
How about this?

04:34.360 --> 04:35.120
Let me think of a way.

04:35.120 --> 04:36.120
I'll get him back,

04:36.180 --> 04:37.750
and then you wait for my message.

04:37.750 --> 04:38.800
Are you sure about this?

04:38.800 --> 04:40.560
Whether I'm sure or not, don't act.

04:40.560 --> 04:41.360
Otherwise, all my previous efforts

04:41.360 --> 04:42.220
will be wasted.

04:42.280 --> 04:42.880
That's it.

04:54.530 --> 04:55.409
Cheng.

04:58.780 --> 05:00.070
You took all of this for yourself.

05:00.070 --> 05:01.750
Do you think you can handle it
all by yourself?

05:01.750 --> 05:02.480
Liu Jinlong?

05:02.910 --> 05:04.710
Didn't see this coming, did you?

05:04.770 --> 05:05.620
Get rid of him.

05:11.220 --> 05:12.100
Attention, Surveillance team.

05:12.100 --> 05:13.300
Delay the operation.

05:13.480 --> 05:15.310
Delay the operation. Hold position.

05:15.310 --> 05:16.360
How long are we delaying?

05:16.360 --> 05:17.760
Wait for further notice.

05:18.270 --> 05:20.160
Who knows how long that'll take?

05:23.350 --> 05:24.480
Something's wrong.

05:25.340 --> 05:26.850
[Signal lost]

05:28.360 --> 05:29.220
What happened?

05:30.240 --> 05:31.240
It's not on my end.

05:34.250 --> 05:34.850
Chief Tan.

05:35.290 --> 05:36.240
We need to act immediately.

05:36.240 --> 05:37.240
But he specifically said

05:37.240 --> 05:38.330
not to go over there.

05:38.330 --> 05:40.030
Jiang Cheng has no reason
to disable the tracker.

05:40.030 --> 05:41.470
He must have been exposed.

05:41.470 --> 05:42.790
Whether Old Scorpion
is there today or not,

05:42.790 --> 05:44.320
we need to act immediately.

05:44.440 --> 05:45.080
If it's too late,

05:45.080 --> 05:46.740
Jiang Cheng will be in danger.

05:53.000 --> 05:54.600
Attention, all teams.

05:55.040 --> 05:56.000
Move out now.

05:56.750 --> 05:57.150
Hurry.

05:58.310 --> 05:59.630
Attention, all units.

05:59.870 --> 06:00.480
These guys

06:00.500 --> 06:02.210
aren't your typical gang—

06:02.630 --> 06:03.480
they're so brutal

06:03.480 --> 06:04.600
it's horrifying.

06:04.720 --> 06:05.980
During the operation,

06:06.430 --> 06:07.720
you must be highly vigilant.

06:07.720 --> 06:08.680
Understood.

06:23.220 --> 06:24.290
The sentries have been taken out.

06:24.290 --> 06:25.880
Breach the factory. Move!

06:31.210 --> 06:33.810
All teams advance step by step
according to the plan.

06:33.810 --> 06:35.270
The factory has been modified.

06:35.270 --> 06:37.159
The layout is complex.
Leave no stone unturned.

06:37.159 --> 06:39.720
Look out for our man during the operation.

06:39.750 --> 06:40.240
Male,

06:40.360 --> 06:41.200
31 years old.

06:41.220 --> 06:41.950
Name:

06:42.050 --> 06:42.890
Jiang Cheng.

07:05.670 --> 07:06.670
Does it feel good?

07:08.430 --> 07:09.240
Cheng.

07:13.600 --> 07:15.330
It's about to feel even better.

07:17.610 --> 07:19.530
Drag that lapdog over here.

07:24.090 --> 07:25.480
Freeze! Freeze! Freeze!

07:25.480 --> 07:28.190
Freeze! Freeze! Freeze!

07:28.370 --> 07:29.980
Freeze! Freeze!

07:34.070 --> 07:34.830
Command vehicle,

07:34.830 --> 07:36.120
we found a hidden door leading
to an underground factory.

07:36.120 --> 07:37.270
Move!

07:39.850 --> 07:43.730
Freeze! Freeze! Freeze!

07:43.870 --> 07:44.670
Police! Stop!

07:48.670 --> 07:49.670
Command vehicle,

07:50.230 --> 07:51.750
there's no sign of our man.

07:51.750 --> 07:53.590
Expand the search area and keep looking.

07:53.590 --> 07:54.120
Yes, sir.

07:55.280 --> 07:55.830
Take them all away!

07:55.830 --> 07:56.360
Yes, sir.

07:56.490 --> 07:58.130
Report: Team A has no target.

07:58.159 --> 07:59.320
Reporting, he's not here, either.

07:59.320 --> 08:00.490
Team D has no target.

08:00.870 --> 08:01.870
Send reinforcements.

08:01.870 --> 08:03.480
Surveillance team,
reinforce the East Zone.

08:03.480 --> 08:04.190
Let's go.

08:09.530 --> 08:10.330
Do it.

08:10.480 --> 08:12.750
I... I've never killed anyone. Don't...

08:12.750 --> 08:14.430
Do it.

08:14.430 --> 08:15.160
Don't push me.

08:15.160 --> 08:16.920
Hurry up!

08:16.920 --> 08:17.720
Don't push me!

08:20.750 --> 08:21.360
Hurry up!

08:23.240 --> 08:24.480
Cheng. Cheng.

08:24.830 --> 08:25.390
Cheng.

08:25.920 --> 08:27.040
Cheng.

08:27.320 --> 08:29.250
I'm sorry, Cheng.

08:29.780 --> 08:32.100
I... I'm so sorry, Cheng.

08:32.250 --> 08:34.409
Cheng, I'm sorry.

08:35.480 --> 08:36.630
I... I'm sorry.

08:36.929 --> 08:37.530
I…

08:37.549 --> 08:38.789
I'm sorry.

08:39.120 --> 08:40.440
Cheng, I'm sorry.

08:40.440 --> 08:41.510
I'm sorry.

08:51.400 --> 08:53.040
Can't find the satellite phone signal.

08:53.040 --> 08:54.060
We can't determine the location.

08:54.060 --> 08:55.620
A full sweep would take too long.

08:55.620 --> 08:58.080
We need to narrow it down
as much as possible.

08:59.620 --> 09:01.670
The signal disappeared here.

09:01.960 --> 09:02.550
I suggest

09:02.810 --> 09:04.190
starting the investigation

09:04.190 --> 09:06.800
with the most concealed locations,
focusing on those

09:06.800 --> 09:09.080
that offer the best cover
and the easiest routes for retreat.

09:09.080 --> 09:09.510
Okay.

09:17.980 --> 09:20.250
I'm sorry, Cheng.

09:23.360 --> 09:24.360
Does it feel good?

09:26.370 --> 09:29.090
Does it feel good
to be tortured by your bro?

09:31.880 --> 09:33.520
I really don't understand.

09:33.540 --> 09:35.300
What are you doing this for?

09:37.180 --> 09:39.770
Are you worthy of Boss He's trust?

09:41.520 --> 09:44.760
Are you worthy of Dahua and your buddies?

09:47.120 --> 09:48.200
Or

09:49.970 --> 09:52.890
are you worthy of being a cop?

09:59.770 --> 10:00.650
Dahua.

10:01.160 --> 10:03.400
Did you know our Cheng is a cop?

10:03.420 --> 10:04.690
A cop.

10:08.630 --> 10:09.630
Cheng.

10:10.200 --> 10:13.630
I've always been curious about one thing.

10:14.750 --> 10:17.870
When Yao Weihai took his last breath,

10:19.340 --> 10:21.810
how did you feel?

10:26.190 --> 10:27.990
I only have 2 things to ask of you.

10:28.120 --> 10:28.710
First,

10:29.020 --> 10:30.480
stay firm with your faith.

10:30.790 --> 10:31.250
Second,

10:32.000 --> 10:32.660
stay alive.

10:34.550 --> 10:35.280
Jiang Cheng,

10:35.700 --> 10:37.360
you really didn't let me down.

10:50.360 --> 10:52.420
These 3 locations meet the criteria.

10:53.360 --> 10:55.000
But they are quite far apart.

10:55.210 --> 10:57.540
We don't have time
to check them one by one.

11:00.910 --> 11:01.320
Here.

11:03.350 --> 11:04.610
How confident are you?

11:06.130 --> 11:07.110
Fifty percent.

11:12.870 --> 11:13.270
Okay.

11:14.710 --> 11:15.840
Let's take a gamble.

11:18.030 --> 11:18.890
That's enough.

11:20.030 --> 11:20.830
Cut the throat

11:21.380 --> 11:23.380
to this length.

11:23.410 --> 11:23.980
I...

11:24.000 --> 11:24.840
I won't do it.

11:29.520 --> 11:31.290
Cheng, I don't want to die.

11:31.320 --> 11:32.960
Save me, Cheng.

11:33.360 --> 11:35.030
Cheng, save me.

11:35.050 --> 11:37.840
I don't want to die, Cheng.

11:39.790 --> 11:41.840
Save me, Cheng!

11:41.840 --> 11:43.840
Cheng.

11:49.730 --> 11:50.330
Cheng.

11:50.890 --> 11:52.330
Cheng.

11:52.870 --> 11:54.550
D-Don't blame me, Cheng.

11:55.150 --> 11:57.270
D-Don't blame me.

11:57.290 --> 11:58.050
Cheng.

11:58.200 --> 12:00.080
Cheng, don't blame me.

12:15.500 --> 12:17.270
Did you kill Jiang Cheng? Fall back!

12:17.270 --> 12:18.800
The police are breaking in!

12:20.970 --> 12:21.730
Don't move!

12:28.600 --> 12:29.270
Freeze!

12:34.680 --> 12:35.810
Identify yourself.

12:38.150 --> 12:39.670
Former deputy captain

12:39.840 --> 12:41.030
of Haizhou

12:41.960 --> 12:43.480
Fengzhou District

12:43.720 --> 12:45.720
Criminal Investigation Brigade 2,

12:46.460 --> 12:47.500
member

12:47.740 --> 12:50.700
of the 8/17 Case task force, Special Ops—

12:51.750 --> 12:52.550
Jiang Cheng.

12:54.960 --> 12:55.800
Code name:

12:56.650 --> 12:57.530
Cangfeng.

13:02.160 --> 13:02.890
Are you okay?

13:04.840 --> 13:06.460
Hurry up! Hurry up.

13:06.490 --> 13:07.060
Hurry.

13:07.960 --> 13:08.630
Jin,

13:09.140 --> 13:10.850
I think I'm dying.

13:10.960 --> 13:11.790
Bullshit!

13:11.790 --> 13:12.720
Hurry up.

13:12.720 --> 13:13.720
Call an ambulance!

13:13.720 --> 13:14.810
Call the medic, hurry.

13:14.810 --> 13:15.300
Go!

13:17.000 --> 13:17.790
Jiang Cheng.

13:18.440 --> 13:19.170
Jiang Cheng.

13:21.150 --> 13:21.790
Jin.

13:22.960 --> 13:23.670
Can you

13:23.990 --> 13:25.320
give me a kiss

13:25.580 --> 13:26.950
to comfort me?

13:26.970 --> 13:28.000
Get lost!

13:30.390 --> 13:31.250
What happened?

13:33.340 --> 13:34.140
Jiang Cheng.

13:34.480 --> 13:35.010
Jiang...

13:35.480 --> 13:36.210
Jiang Cheng.

13:36.360 --> 13:37.090
Are you okay?

14:00.100 --> 14:01.050
Jin.

14:02.100 --> 14:03.220
I was wrong.

14:04.550 --> 14:05.610
I was really wrong.

14:07.020 --> 14:08.020
I know.

14:08.820 --> 14:09.750
I know

14:09.770 --> 14:11.740
you'll be mad at me.

14:12.840 --> 14:15.270
What you hate most is being lied to.

14:17.240 --> 14:18.080
I'm sorry.

14:18.750 --> 14:19.480
I'm sorry.

14:19.480 --> 14:20.910
Will you forgive me?

14:21.950 --> 14:22.870
I've hated...

14:23.710 --> 14:25.290
I've hated you for 5 years.

14:25.600 --> 14:27.730
Did you know I've hated you
for 5 years?

14:40.110 --> 14:41.030
You'll be fine.

14:42.220 --> 14:44.150
Professor Jiang, you are awesome!

14:44.270 --> 14:45.120
If it weren't for you today,

14:45.120 --> 14:46.200
we couldn't have

14:46.200 --> 14:47.390
locked onto their location so quickly.

14:47.390 --> 14:48.150
You nailed it on the first try.

14:48.150 --> 14:49.600
You are awesome.

14:51.140 --> 14:52.670
Some people are just lucky.

14:52.670 --> 14:55.080
It has nothing to do with luck.

14:55.080 --> 14:56.140
I think, Professor Jiang,

14:56.140 --> 14:57.970
this comes from the experience
you've accumulated over the years.

14:57.970 --> 14:58.860
It's absolutely—

14:58.860 --> 14:59.780
Keep your eyes on the screen.

14:59.780 --> 15:01.080
What are you so excited about?

15:01.080 --> 15:01.740
But this...

15:09.550 --> 15:10.550
Team A reporting.

15:10.630 --> 15:12.200
Drug makers are basically under control.

15:12.200 --> 15:13.420
The target boss is not seen.

15:13.420 --> 15:14.880
Okay, Cangfeng has been found.

15:14.880 --> 15:15.790
All teams, attention.

15:15.790 --> 15:17.120
Focus on searching for the prime culprit.

15:17.120 --> 15:18.550
Make sure to catch He Wu.

15:18.670 --> 15:19.200
Yes, sir.

15:19.740 --> 15:21.270
He Wu hasn't been found yet?

15:21.450 --> 15:22.380
We will find him.

15:24.110 --> 15:25.580
Surveillance team 1, Surveillance team 1.

15:25.580 --> 15:26.130
Copy that.

15:26.130 --> 15:27.930
Bring Comrade Jiang Cheng back.

15:30.480 --> 15:31.080
Copy that.

15:34.440 --> 15:34.970
Let's go.

15:43.790 --> 15:44.720
Feeling better?

15:46.100 --> 15:46.770
Junior,

15:46.800 --> 15:47.680
leave him to me.

15:48.870 --> 15:49.600
Jiang Cheng,

15:50.200 --> 15:51.590
you are suspected
of murdering the 8/17 Case

15:51.590 --> 15:53.060
task force leader Yao Weihai

15:53.060 --> 15:54.440
and officer Meng Junfeng.

15:54.440 --> 15:57.100
Please come back
with us for the investigation.

16:00.490 --> 16:02.290
I know you're feeling terrible,

16:02.680 --> 16:04.640
but we have to follow the rules.

16:05.300 --> 16:06.900
You can talk when we get back.

16:11.550 --> 16:12.030
Okay.

16:16.520 --> 16:17.190
I'm sorry.

16:21.270 --> 16:22.030
Jiang Cheng!

16:22.360 --> 16:23.240
Jiang Cheng.

16:24.500 --> 16:25.380
Jiang Cheng!

16:25.560 --> 16:26.980
Jiang Cheng, open the door!

16:26.980 --> 16:27.860
Jiang Cheng!

16:39.490 --> 16:40.570
You left me here.

16:41.260 --> 16:43.060
You want to sacrifice me, right?

16:43.450 --> 16:45.380
I've destroyed the surveillance.

16:45.630 --> 16:46.750
Tell me right now,

16:47.250 --> 16:49.180
how am I supposed to get out of here?

16:53.030 --> 16:55.270
Split up. One on each side.

17:27.800 --> 17:28.510
He Wu!

17:28.540 --> 17:29.780
You won't escape.

17:30.360 --> 17:31.120
Jiang Cheng!

17:32.750 --> 17:34.240
I trusted you so much,

17:34.310 --> 17:36.310
but you actually betrayed your bro?

17:36.350 --> 17:37.640
Who's your bro?

17:38.790 --> 17:39.440
He Wu.

17:39.740 --> 17:41.740
I advise you not to walk into a dead end.

17:41.740 --> 17:42.940
If you surrender now,

17:42.950 --> 17:44.920
you still have a chance
to atone for your sins.

17:44.920 --> 17:45.880
Atone?

17:46.220 --> 17:47.680
What's the use of atoning?

17:48.290 --> 17:49.680
But you, Jiang Cheng,

17:51.030 --> 17:51.830
go to hell

17:51.830 --> 17:53.640
and atone to my brother He Wen.

17:54.830 --> 17:55.680
He

17:56.480 --> 17:57.680
treated you like a real brother.

17:57.680 --> 17:59.950
Before he died,
he even asked me to take care of you.

17:59.950 --> 18:00.740
But you?

18:01.370 --> 18:02.720
Did you do right by him?

18:03.590 --> 18:04.350
And,

18:04.880 --> 18:07.010
you can't explain
Yao Weihai's death.

18:08.300 --> 18:09.690
And Junfeng.

18:10.150 --> 18:11.550
They are all dead now!

18:13.640 --> 18:14.970
You, an undercover cop,

18:15.510 --> 18:17.110
are really interesting.

18:20.030 --> 18:21.000
For 5 years...

18:21.350 --> 18:23.550
For 5 whole years, I called you brother.

18:23.920 --> 18:25.580
And now you're here to kill me.

18:26.110 --> 18:26.880
Okay.

18:27.750 --> 18:30.810
Today, I will send you,
the undercover cop, on your way!

19:04.830 --> 19:06.310
Surveillance team 1, Surveillance team 1.

19:06.310 --> 19:07.640
Report your situation.

19:08.110 --> 19:09.550
Surveillance team 1, Surveillance team 1.

19:09.550 --> 19:10.880
Report your situation.

19:11.710 --> 19:14.110
Surveillance team 1, Surveillance team 1.

21:02.150 --> 21:04.550
Tell me where Old Scorpion is!

21:12.570 --> 21:13.570
Stop laughing!

21:30.240 --> 21:31.570
Hold on tight!

21:39.590 --> 21:40.320
Jiang Cheng.

21:42.680 --> 21:43.200
Grab it.

22:17.200 --> 22:18.130
Hurry. Let's go.

22:20.680 --> 22:21.440
Are you okay?

22:27.210 --> 22:28.540
Hold on a little longer.

22:28.860 --> 22:29.400
Almost...

22:29.400 --> 22:30.200
Almost there.

22:30.400 --> 22:31.130
Jiang Cheng!

22:31.240 --> 22:31.970
Jiang Cheng!

22:32.030 --> 22:32.920
Jiang Cheng.

22:33.110 --> 22:33.770
Jiang Cheng.

22:33.770 --> 22:34.360
Jiang Cheng.

22:34.360 --> 22:35.320
Jiang Cheng.

22:36.080 --> 22:36.680
Found him!

22:36.680 --> 22:38.030
Hurry! Hurry.

22:38.140 --> 22:38.900
Over here.

22:38.980 --> 22:39.660
Hurry up.

22:40.030 --> 22:41.000
Hurry up.

22:41.540 --> 22:42.300
Careful.

22:44.030 --> 22:44.790
Lift him up.

23:00.240 --> 23:01.370
Hold his hands down.

23:15.000 --> 23:15.610
Zhou Jin.

23:16.940 --> 23:17.590
Mentor.

23:23.030 --> 23:24.090
There's something

23:24.790 --> 23:26.350
I have to make clear to you.

23:28.440 --> 23:31.200
Because your relationship
with Jiang Cheng is special,

23:31.200 --> 23:32.920
you can't participate in

23:33.960 --> 23:35.690
the following investigation.

23:35.880 --> 23:37.010
This is discipline.

23:37.510 --> 23:38.240
Understand?

23:38.720 --> 23:39.520
I understand.

23:39.680 --> 23:40.940
I'll keep my distance.

23:41.440 --> 23:42.510
This case

23:42.540 --> 23:45.270
is under heavy scrutiny
from all sides right now.

23:45.510 --> 23:46.920
And he is a key witness

23:46.920 --> 23:48.030
in this case.

23:48.270 --> 23:49.480
So the subsequent investigation

23:49.480 --> 23:51.080
might be quite complicated.

23:53.720 --> 23:55.180
Have you told your parents

23:56.480 --> 23:57.590
about Jiang Cheng?

23:58.830 --> 23:59.720
Not yet.

24:00.400 --> 24:01.240
I want to wait

24:01.240 --> 24:02.830
until the investigation is over

24:02.830 --> 24:04.110
and everything is clear

24:04.110 --> 24:05.170
before I tell them.

24:07.160 --> 24:07.890
That's good.

24:10.920 --> 24:12.250
How is Professor Jiang?

24:12.750 --> 24:13.720
What's wrong with him?

24:13.720 --> 24:16.780
He had a fever and took leave to go home.
Didn't you know?

24:16.830 --> 24:17.680
He had a fever?

24:17.870 --> 24:18.670
Look at you.

24:18.690 --> 24:20.280
Why are you asking me?

24:20.310 --> 24:21.750
You are his wife.

24:21.750 --> 24:22.760
Alright, don't just stand there.

24:22.760 --> 24:23.890
Hurry up and go home.

24:31.590 --> 24:32.240
Hansheng.

24:46.990 --> 24:47.710
Hansheng.

25:19.140 --> 25:20.380
Why did you drink?

25:22.000 --> 25:22.800
Just a little.

25:26.040 --> 25:27.850
Do you come back to get something?

25:27.850 --> 25:28.780
What do you need?

25:28.830 --> 25:29.890
I'll get it for you.

25:30.880 --> 25:32.740
Why would I need to get something?

25:35.570 --> 25:37.710
Aren't you bringing a change of clothes?

25:37.710 --> 25:38.990
I'm not on duty today.

25:39.440 --> 25:40.790
Mentor said you had a fever.

25:40.790 --> 25:42.390
I rushed back to check on you.

25:57.680 --> 25:59.480
Why aren't you saying anything?

25:59.930 --> 26:01.060
Are you drunk?

26:23.720 --> 26:25.090
Don't move. Behave.

26:32.500 --> 26:34.030
Did you take your medicine?

26:35.300 --> 26:35.930
I did.

26:37.690 --> 26:39.220
I woke up drenched in sweat,

26:39.850 --> 26:40.880
so I took a shower.

26:43.930 --> 26:44.890
You're sick,

26:44.920 --> 26:46.030
and you still drank.

26:46.030 --> 26:47.640
Then you took medicine after drinking,

26:47.640 --> 26:49.480
and even took a shower with a fever?

26:49.480 --> 26:50.410
Jiang Hansheng,

26:50.970 --> 26:52.450
do you have a death wish?

26:56.640 --> 26:57.170
How is it?

26:59.640 --> 27:01.500
Don't you know if you have a fever?

27:10.280 --> 27:11.240
37.6 degrees.

27:11.500 --> 27:12.430
It's a low fever.

27:19.070 --> 27:20.730
You didn't even dry your hair.

27:22.090 --> 27:24.750
Don't you know
you'll have a headache tomorrow?

27:54.740 --> 27:56.420
I'll make you tomato and eggs,

27:56.460 --> 27:59.320
and maybe some stir-fried pork
with green peppers.

27:59.460 --> 28:02.460
Anything more complicated than that,
I can't handle.

28:05.110 --> 28:07.040
Are you going to eat with me at home?

28:09.350 --> 28:11.210
You're not going to the hospital?

28:12.370 --> 28:13.900
I just came back from there.

28:21.960 --> 28:23.020
How is Jiang Cheng?

28:25.350 --> 28:26.350
He's fine.

28:26.850 --> 28:28.350
There's someone taking care of him.

28:28.350 --> 28:30.080
I should keep my distance, too.

28:58.440 --> 28:59.400
Are you drunk,

29:00.290 --> 29:01.820
or are you not feeling well?

29:09.140 --> 29:10.140
It is boiling.

29:14.380 --> 29:15.310
Jiang Hansheng.

29:15.830 --> 29:16.480
I'm here.

29:18.720 --> 29:20.330
If you keep hugging me like this,

29:20.330 --> 29:20.860
we're going to have another case

29:20.860 --> 29:23.320
of carbon monoxide poisoning
in this house.

29:44.310 --> 29:46.370
If you want to talk about Jiang Cheng,

29:46.550 --> 29:47.550
you can talk to me.

29:49.410 --> 29:50.170
I don't mind.

29:53.660 --> 29:54.590
I'm fine.

29:54.920 --> 29:55.640
Really.

30:05.110 --> 30:06.040
Jiang Hansheng.

30:08.440 --> 30:09.310
Are you angry?

30:09.550 --> 30:10.720
Of course I am.

30:11.550 --> 30:12.680
You can bite me back.

30:13.120 --> 30:14.560
Why would I bite you?

30:16.160 --> 30:16.810
Zhou Jin,

30:18.240 --> 30:20.370
you can treat me without any scruples.

30:20.540 --> 30:21.830
You can say whatever you want

30:21.830 --> 30:23.230
and do whatever you want.

30:24.240 --> 30:25.240
Anything is fine.

30:27.780 --> 30:30.440
You don't need to consider
whether I can bear it.

30:30.960 --> 30:31.960
I'm your husband.

30:32.720 --> 30:34.850
We're married—we should be like this.

30:35.310 --> 30:36.240
No holding back,

30:36.840 --> 30:39.640
no pretending.
You don't have to hold back with me.

30:41.310 --> 30:42.030
So,

30:42.420 --> 30:44.030
you can do whatever you want.

30:45.110 --> 30:46.110
It's just that...

30:47.540 --> 30:48.500
it really hurts.

30:56.130 --> 30:56.990
It was my fault.

30:57.690 --> 30:58.750
It was my fault.

31:00.070 --> 31:01.330
That's not your fault.

31:01.880 --> 31:03.080
There are some things

31:03.780 --> 31:04.930
I might not do well.

31:07.680 --> 31:10.000
But you do many things very well.

31:11.590 --> 31:12.480
You are calm,

31:12.750 --> 31:13.440
sharp,

31:14.580 --> 31:15.380
and talented.

31:17.680 --> 31:20.340
There are many things
that seem very difficult,

31:20.510 --> 31:21.480
but with you,

31:22.480 --> 31:24.210
you can always find a solution.

31:29.230 --> 31:30.120
I'm greedy.

32:09.400 --> 32:10.930
It's not this pocket watch.

32:12.160 --> 32:13.890
I've seen a more beautiful one.

32:15.560 --> 32:16.950
On that pocket watch,

32:19.630 --> 32:21.430
there was a pine branch pattern.

32:22.130 --> 32:23.590
It was polished brightly.

32:25.350 --> 32:27.210
Inside it, there was a little girl

32:28.750 --> 32:30.550
smiling at you with curved eyes.

32:33.220 --> 32:35.420
I think this one is also very beautiful.

32:36.700 --> 32:38.110
Can you show it to me?

32:38.480 --> 32:39.270
No,

32:39.400 --> 32:40.510
it's not beautiful enough.

32:40.510 --> 32:41.370
It's not right.

32:42.190 --> 32:43.190
It's not right.

32:44.570 --> 32:46.300
It's not good-looking enough.

32:47.650 --> 32:49.110
Not good-looking enough.

32:49.510 --> 32:50.350
Did I

32:50.350 --> 32:52.510
do something to upset you?

32:57.710 --> 32:59.990
I asked you to investigate Jiang Cheng.

33:01.200 --> 33:03.390
But you didn't find out that Jiang Cheng

33:03.390 --> 33:04.700
knows Officer Zhou?

33:05.750 --> 33:07.830
Or did you know Jiang Cheng had a problem

33:07.830 --> 33:10.100
but didn't tell me?

33:11.430 --> 33:12.430
Y-you should

33:13.300 --> 33:15.410
ask Boss He about him.

33:16.170 --> 33:17.640
Do you like Jiang Cheng?

33:18.990 --> 33:19.920
He's quite cute.

33:20.130 --> 33:22.190
Really, I also think he's quite cute.

33:22.310 --> 33:22.930
Tell me the truth.

33:22.930 --> 33:23.830
Don't be like this.

33:23.830 --> 33:24.830
Tell me the truth.

33:25.480 --> 33:28.160
This is not the answer I want!

33:30.200 --> 33:32.720
You lied to me.

33:45.880 --> 33:46.940
As expected of you.

33:47.860 --> 33:48.970
That's enough.

33:50.090 --> 33:51.160
Don't push me.

34:03.140 --> 34:03.960
You know what?

34:04.850 --> 34:07.090
Only you dare to treat me like this.

34:14.219 --> 34:14.820
Qiu Ye.

34:15.960 --> 34:17.000
Do you know why,

34:18.330 --> 34:20.389
no matter what huge mistake you make,

34:21.100 --> 34:22.560
I will always forgive you?

34:24.440 --> 34:25.070
I'm sorry.

34:34.440 --> 34:35.040
I'm tired.

34:40.590 --> 34:41.360
I'm tired.

34:47.420 --> 34:48.139
Tired.

34:52.159 --> 34:56.150
[Three days later]

35:03.520 --> 35:06.070
Jiang Cheng's interrogation
should have started.

35:06.070 --> 35:07.200
I heard it's at 9:30.

35:10.030 --> 35:11.590
Zhao Ping and I went to Jingzhou.

35:11.590 --> 35:12.860
We missed so much.

35:12.880 --> 35:15.530
We didn't participate
in such a big operation at all.

35:15.530 --> 35:16.490
What a pity.

35:17.640 --> 35:19.900
What has Zhao Ping been busy with lately?

35:20.190 --> 35:22.450
He's sorting out the materials
for the Crime Research Lab.

35:22.450 --> 35:23.340
Director Wang

35:23.370 --> 35:24.970
writes a lot of things by hand

35:25.120 --> 35:26.030
and on those

35:26.030 --> 35:27.320
lined papers.

35:27.440 --> 35:29.690
The handwriting is so wild
that it's almost as hard to read

35:29.690 --> 35:31.220
as a doctor's handwriting.

35:32.040 --> 35:34.470
Chief Tan asked him
to sort them out and print them.

35:34.470 --> 35:36.400
That will keep him busy for a while.

35:45.360 --> 35:46.360
Behave yourself.

35:46.590 --> 35:47.240
Sit down.

35:50.570 --> 35:51.250
Are you messing around?

35:51.250 --> 35:52.510
Where are you looking?

35:53.710 --> 35:54.670
We brought you here today

35:54.670 --> 35:55.510
to ask about

35:55.510 --> 35:57.930
Jiang Cheng's situation
while he was serving his sentence.

35:57.930 --> 35:59.690
I heard you are very familiar
with him, right?

35:59.690 --> 36:00.730
Jiang Cheng?

36:01.370 --> 36:02.970
T-Then let me ask in advance.

36:03.320 --> 36:04.880
If I answer truthfully

36:05.070 --> 36:06.050
and cooperate with the investigation,

36:06.050 --> 36:07.710
can I get a commuted sentence?

36:07.880 --> 36:10.540
It depends on
whether it meets the regulations.

36:10.950 --> 36:12.230
Whether it's useful or not,

36:12.230 --> 36:14.480
as long as there's a beautiful officer
who chats with me for a while,

36:14.480 --> 36:15.880
I'll say whatever I know.

36:16.880 --> 36:19.180
Obstructing police officers
from executing their duties

36:19.180 --> 36:20.710
will be severely punished.

36:22.970 --> 36:24.090
Here are 10 photos.

36:24.250 --> 36:25.650
Which one is Jiang Cheng?

36:28.330 --> 36:29.670
He... he's not in any of them.

36:29.670 --> 36:31.070
He's not in the first row.

36:32.860 --> 36:33.860
What about these?

36:34.470 --> 36:35.200
That one.

36:35.230 --> 36:36.030
The middle one.

36:36.030 --> 36:36.880
That one, yes.

36:36.880 --> 36:37.480
Is it him?

36:37.480 --> 36:37.510
That one. It can't be wrong.

36:37.510 --> 36:38.950
That one. It can't be wrong.

36:38.950 --> 36:40.990
I used to be in the same cell as him.

36:41.840 --> 36:42.590
Then tell us

36:42.620 --> 36:43.790
how

36:43.810 --> 36:44.810
and when you meet?

36:45.910 --> 36:47.110
I can't

36:47.110 --> 36:48.510
remember the exact time.

36:48.670 --> 36:50.480
Anyway, I remember when he first came in,

36:50.480 --> 36:52.010
he was in the same cell as me.

36:52.440 --> 36:53.320
Well,

36:53.350 --> 36:55.310
at first, he didn't know anyone

36:55.510 --> 36:57.090
and wouldn't talk to anyone.

36:57.090 --> 36:58.800
So I wasn't familiar with him, either.

36:58.800 --> 37:00.800
But you know, this kind of place

37:00.830 --> 37:02.830
can never keep any secrets.

37:03.210 --> 37:04.850
On his very first day here,

37:05.070 --> 37:07.670
everyone knew he used to be a cop.

37:08.330 --> 37:09.360
None of the people in here

37:09.360 --> 37:11.510
don't hate cops.

37:11.620 --> 37:13.270
Right? And he was new.

37:13.290 --> 37:14.350
It was his first time in prison.

37:14.350 --> 37:15.750
So the boss here

37:15.770 --> 37:16.690
often

37:16.840 --> 37:18.240
got people to beat him up.

37:19.310 --> 37:20.410
Jiang Cheng

37:20.440 --> 37:22.290
was kind of a coward at first.

37:22.520 --> 37:24.380
He didn't fight back when beaten.

37:24.520 --> 37:26.470
We even laughed at him behind his back,

37:26.470 --> 37:27.670
saying he was the type

37:27.820 --> 37:30.340
who couldn't act tough
without his uniform.

37:31.710 --> 37:32.710
Since he never spoke up

37:32.710 --> 37:34.070
after getting hit,

37:34.070 --> 37:35.130
the others thought

37:35.190 --> 37:35.960
he was a wimp,

37:35.980 --> 37:37.960
so they had people beat him up every day.

37:37.960 --> 37:39.230
Honestly,

37:39.230 --> 37:39.960
with something like this,

37:39.960 --> 37:42.500
if you just swallow your pride
and admit fault,

37:42.500 --> 37:43.750
it'll blow over.

37:44.000 --> 37:46.280
I even tried to talk him into it
behind the scenes a few times—

37:46.280 --> 37:48.470
told him to just bow his head
and let it go.

37:48.470 --> 37:51.470
But his temper is really not great.

37:51.500 --> 37:52.430
He's stubborn.

37:52.510 --> 37:54.340
He didn't say a word
and didn't admit defeat

37:54.340 --> 37:56.000
after being beaten like that.

37:56.220 --> 37:57.970
But then again,

37:58.320 --> 38:01.150
you can't push people too far, right?

38:01.410 --> 38:03.670
Tolerating it once or twice is one thing.

38:03.690 --> 38:05.070
Who can tolerate it forever?

38:05.070 --> 38:06.600
How long did he tolerate it?

38:07.170 --> 38:08.570
Probably for about...

38:08.850 --> 38:09.770
about a month.

38:10.230 --> 38:11.690
Someone came to visit him.

38:12.350 --> 38:13.410
After he came back that day,

38:13.410 --> 38:14.740
he wasn't acting right.

38:15.490 --> 38:17.550
He didn't talk and ignored everyone.

38:20.050 --> 38:28.270
[2012]

38:37.630 --> 38:38.590
Jiang Cheng!

38:38.940 --> 38:40.100
Go sit over there.

39:37.880 --> 39:39.410
What happened to your face?

39:46.930 --> 39:47.860
Why?

39:54.930 --> 39:55.660
Jiang Cheng.

40:00.320 --> 40:02.450
I don't believe you'd be hiding drugs.

40:04.720 --> 40:05.780
Someone set you up,

40:06.680 --> 40:07.320
right?

40:11.150 --> 40:12.020
Say something.

40:13.960 --> 40:15.690
I'll believe whatever you say.

40:19.820 --> 40:21.330
Say something.

40:22.980 --> 40:24.860
Was someone trying to set you up?

40:30.330 --> 40:32.170
When did you turn into this?

40:37.170 --> 40:38.850
How did I not notice at all?

40:43.920 --> 40:45.360
If there's nothing else,

40:46.200 --> 40:47.860
let's leave it at that for now.

40:48.420 --> 40:49.390
Dad had a stroke.

40:55.330 --> 40:57.570
Except for a little problem with his leg,

40:57.570 --> 40:58.970
everything else is fine.

41:05.080 --> 41:06.880
He asked me to pass you a message.

41:10.640 --> 41:12.100
It's never too late to turn

41:13.080 --> 41:13.940
over a new leaf.

41:26.650 --> 41:28.180
Nothing else to say, right?

41:34.460 --> 41:36.120
The stuff for our engagement—

41:38.840 --> 41:40.040
I'll return it to you.

41:42.920 --> 41:44.580
The banquet will be canceled.

41:46.080 --> 41:47.880
The rings will be returned, too.

41:53.590 --> 41:54.400
And,

41:58.490 --> 42:00.020
the promises you made to me—

42:03.620 --> 42:04.970
I'll forget them all.

42:16.000 --> 42:16.690
Up to you.
